caption.center: DAVID POWELL, Petitioner(s) v. ARENA HOTEL, Respondent(s).

opinion.opinion_text: Petitioner's "Verified Motion to Reinstate Established Timeliness Proved Up of Case w/i 15 Days" filed January 4, 2006, and "Verified Motion Caption Defect of Parties Form; Extension of Time; Stay" filed January 6, 2006, are hereby dismissed on the Court's own motion based on petitioner's failure to timely file a proper certificate of service in accordance with this Court's order dated January 19, 2006.
